Buket Aydın (born 1 January 1985) is a Turkish TV presenter.
She later completed the Kuşdili Speaker and Presenter Course in Kadıköy with good grades.
After a year as a news anchor on a private radio station, she joined the Kanaltürk channel where she served as the sports bulletin announcer and later as the host of the main news bulletins.
After leaving Kanaltürk, she transferred to TRT Türk and served as a presenter.
In April 2011, Buket Aydın transferred to NTV, which was recently restructured, and started to serve as news presenter.
